They'll often say this.

00:10:14.090 --> 00:10:17.080 align:middle line:84%
These things are stealthy
in the extreme frequently.

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:19.400 align:middle line:84%
They're very quiet,
often easy to miss.

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:21.040 align:middle line:90%
But there they are.

