00:20:45.690 --> 00:20:47.310 align:middle line:10%
where it really gets going.

00:20:47.310 --> 00:20:50.580 align:middle line:10%
The 19th century, the century
of the American Civil War

00:20:50.580 --> 00:20:54.480 align:middle line:10%
and Napoleon, that's
where humanity really,

00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:58.780 align:middle line:10%
truly began transforming this
world: Railroads, the telegraph.

00:20:58.780 --> 00:21:02.190 align:middle line:10%
There's some instant
communication for you.

00:21:02.190 --> 00:21:06.490 align:middle line:10%
Global shipping and all of the
beginnings of the stock market,

00:21:06.490 --> 00:21:08.770 align:middle line:10%
and that's stage 3.

00:21:08.770 --> 00:21:11.200 align:middle line:10%
It's the world we
were all born into.

00:21:11.200 --> 00:21:13.570 align:middle line:90%
And it's a great world.

00:21:13.570 --> 00:21:15.280 align:middle line:90%
It was a great world.

00:21:15.280 --> 00:21:16.840 align:middle line:10%
It was a great run.

00:21:16.840 --> 00:21:20.960 align:middle line:10%
Much shorter run
than stages 1 or 2.

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:22.520 align:middle line:10%
They're speeding up.

00:21:22.520 --> 00:21:25.890 align:middle line:10%
And now, we're moving
into, well, I don't know.

00:21:25.890 --> 00:21:27.710 align:middle line:10%
I don't know what
stage 4 is going to be.

00:21:27.710 --> 00:21:30.030 align:middle line:84%
But it's not going to
be the same as stage 3.

00:21:30.030 --> 00:21:31.610 align:middle line:90%
That's a guarantee.

00:21:31.610 --> 00:21:34.070 align:middle line:10%
Something radically different.

00:21:34.070 --> 00:21:37.320 align:middle line:10%
It's not just one little
thing that's changing.

00:21:37.320 --> 00:21:41.040 align:middle line:84%
It's, as I was saying, AI
embedded into our world.

00:21:41.040 --> 00:21:43.670 align:middle line:84%
And we're only at
the beginning of AI.

00:21:43.670 --> 00:21:44.720 align:middle line:90%
We all know.

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:46.430 align:middle line:10%
How far can it go?

00:21:46.430 --> 00:21:48.125 align:middle line:10%
Whose job is at risk?

00:21:48.125 --> 00:21:50.500 align:middle line:10%
You know, every one of us
speakers here, we wonder this--

00:21:50.500 --> 00:21:52.720 align:middle line:10%
I wonder-- I mean, really, I do.

00:21:52.720 --> 00:21:54.720 align:middle line:10%
One day, you're not going
to need a guy like me.

00:21:54.720 --> 00:21:57.060 align:middle line:10%
You can just ask your AI
for something about UFOs.

00:21:57.060 --> 00:21:59.010 align:middle line:10%
And it may do a
better job than I do.

00:21:59.010 --> 00:22:02.020 align:middle line:10%
I hope-- not yet, not yet.

00:22:02.020 --> 00:22:04.480 align:middle line:90%
But I feel like John Henry.

00:22:04.480 --> 00:22:06.860 align:middle line:84%
Remember John Henry,
the steel-driving man?

00:22:06.860 --> 00:22:10.510 align:middle line:84%
They come up with a way to drive
steel for the railroads that's

00:22:10.510 --> 00:22:11.660 align:middle line:90%
better than a human being.

00:22:11.660 --> 00:22:13.660 align:middle line:90%
John Henry was real strong.

00:22:13.660 --> 00:22:15.830 align:middle line:10%
And he's like, ain't no
machine's going to beat me.

00:22:15.830 --> 00:22:18.440 align:middle line:10%
And so they have a race.

00:22:18.440 --> 00:22:20.260 align:middle line:10%
And he wins.

00:22:20.260 --> 00:22:22.600 align:middle line:10%
But then he dies of a
heart attack, I believe.

00:22:22.600 --> 00:22:25.000 align:middle line:10%
So yeah.

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:30.010 align:middle line:10%
Anyway, Stage 4 is weird
because we don't know,

00:22:30.010 --> 00:22:34.300 align:middle line:10%
but there will be things like
very likely brain computer

00:22:34.300 --> 00:22:35.300 align:middle line:10%
interfaces.

00:22:35.300 --> 00:22:36.670 align:middle line:10%
So that's one thing.

00:22:36.670 --> 00:22:38.540 align:middle line:10%
What's that going to be like?

00:22:38.540 --> 00:22:39.970 align:middle line:10%
Like a little
thing in your brain

00:22:39.970 --> 00:22:43.460 align:middle line:10%
literally feeding
you information,

00:22:43.460 --> 00:22:47.270 align:middle line:10%
taking your thoughts
because it probably

00:22:47.270 --> 00:22:49.760 align:middle line:10%
has got to go both ways.

00:22:49.760 --> 00:22:51.910 align:middle line:10%
That's a little weird.

00:22:51.910 --> 00:22:56.240 align:middle line:10%
It's the whole thing of privacy
just going away forever,

00:22:56.240 --> 00:22:58.340 align:middle line:10%
like forever.

00:22:58.340 --> 00:22:59.910 align:middle line:10%
How are we going to manage that?

00:22:59.910 --> 00:23:01.650 align:middle line:10%
Like, how is that
going to change people?

00:23:01.650 --> 00:23:03.530 align:middle line:10%
You're already
seeing the changes.

00:23:03.530 --> 00:23:05.060 align:middle line:10%
We don't have BCIs in our heads.

00:23:05.060 --> 00:23:09.320 align:middle line:10%
But you're seeing the
effects on the human psyche

00:23:09.320 --> 00:23:12.710 align:middle line:10%
from having less and less
privacy because everyone's

00:23:12.710 --> 00:23:14.920 align:middle line:10%
in a little fish tank now.

00:23:14.920 --> 00:23:16.600 align:middle line:10%
And you got to duck--

00:23:16.600 --> 00:23:19.360 align:middle line:10%
duck so that you don't--

00:23:19.360 --> 00:23:22.120 align:middle line:10%
just stay in your little lane.

00:23:22.120 --> 00:23:23.770 align:middle line:10%
Stay in your lane.

00:23:23.770 --> 00:23:25.840 align:middle line:10%
So that's one thing.

00:23:25.840 --> 00:23:33.430 align:middle line:84%
It's a transformation that is
happening underway right now.

00:23:33.430 --> 00:23:37.690 align:middle line:10%
We're going into this,
as I call, Stage 4.

00:23:37.690 --> 00:23:43.870 align:middle line:10%
And I'll say further that
our species is being shaped

00:23:43.870 --> 00:23:49.600 align:middle line:10%
to conform with the
infrastructure we are creating

00:23:49.600 --> 00:23:53.040 align:middle line:10%
or that is actually now
creating itself almost.

00:23:53.040 --> 00:23:55.050 align:middle line:10%
This is something--
I actually said this

00:23:55.050 --> 00:23:58.140 align:middle line:10%
on my website a few months ago.

00:23:58.140 --> 00:24:00.630 align:middle line:10%
And I haven't really
fully worked it out.

00:24:00.630 --> 00:24:05.260 align:middle line:10%
But I'm quite convinced of the
phrase, we serve the system.

00:24:05.260 --> 00:24:06.390 align:middle line:10%
We serve the system.

00:24:06.390 --> 00:24:07.390 align:middle line:10%
And what does that mean?

00:24:07.390 --> 00:24:10.020 align:middle line:10%
Well, I realize, we've--

00:24:10.020 --> 00:24:13.830 align:middle line:10%
throughout our history, we've
created systems of existence

00:24:13.830 --> 00:24:16.620 align:middle line:10%
to serve our needs, so we think.

00:24:16.620 --> 00:24:21.780 align:middle line:10%
But the reality is that a
human being must conform

00:24:21.780 --> 00:24:24.720 align:middle line:10%
to the rules of the system
that he or she is in

00:24:24.720 --> 00:24:26.220 align:middle line:10%
or you pay a penalty.

00:24:26.220 --> 00:24:28.410 align:middle line:84%
In ancient times, when
you're a hunter and gatherer,

00:24:28.410 --> 00:24:30.270 align:middle line:84%
the system was your
natural environment.

00:24:30.270 --> 00:24:32.730 align:middle line:10%
And you better
adhere to the rules,

00:24:32.730 --> 00:24:35.280 align:middle line:10%
like defend yourself
against wild animals,

00:24:35.280 --> 00:24:36.900 align:middle line:10%
or you're going to die.

00:24:36.900 --> 00:24:39.240 align:middle line:10%
Build a shelter, or
you're going to die.

00:24:39.240 --> 00:24:42.820 align:middle line:10%
There are certain rules that you
have to follow in that system.

00:24:42.820 --> 00:24:43.930 align:middle line:10%
And we did a great job.

00:24:43.930 --> 00:24:44.730 align:middle line:10%
And we did it.

00:24:44.730 --> 00:24:46.800 align:middle line:10%
And then we started
developing a kind

00:24:46.800 --> 00:24:49.950 align:middle line:10%
of an artificial
environment with Stage 2,

00:24:49.950 --> 00:24:53.560 align:middle line:10%
where we're controlling
animals now.

00:24:53.560 --> 00:24:55.220 align:middle line:10%
We never did that before.

00:24:55.220 --> 00:24:57.170 align:middle line:10%
We're like, cows, you're
working for us now.

00:24:57.170 --> 00:24:57.680 align:middle line:10%
We're going to grow you.

00:24:57.680 --> 00:24:58.490 align:middle line:10%
We're going to keep you here.

00:24:58.490 --> 00:24:59.240 align:middle line:10%
We're going to feed you.

00:24:59.240 --> 00:25:00.448 align:middle line:10%
We're going to eat you later.

00:25:00.448 --> 00:25:02.200 align:middle line:10%
But you're going
to live with us.

00:25:02.200 --> 00:25:04.130 align:middle line:10%
Wolves, you're going
to become dogs.

00:25:04.130 --> 00:25:05.668 align:middle line:10%
Chickens, get over here.

00:25:05.668 --> 00:25:07.460 align:middle line:10%
Plants, we're going to
remake you and grow.

00:25:07.460 --> 00:25:09.335 align:middle line:10%
You're going to become
wheat and all of that.

00:25:09.335 --> 00:25:10.900 align:middle line:10%
So we just take it for granted.

00:25:10.900 --> 00:25:13.310 align:middle line:10%
We control this natural world.

00:25:13.310 --> 00:25:16.540 align:middle line:10%
And we've created over
these various stages--

00:25:16.540 --> 00:25:17.968 align:middle line:10%
look what we're in.

00:25:17.968 --> 00:25:19.010 align:middle line:10%
We're in the Luxor Hotel.

00:25:19.010 --> 00:25:20.320 align:middle line:10%
Could you imagine
what would be like

00:25:20.320 --> 00:25:21.880 align:middle line:10%
if we took one of those
hunters and gatherers

00:25:21.880 --> 00:25:22.970 align:middle line:10%
and brought them here?

00:25:22.970 --> 00:25:24.710 align:middle line:10%
They would lose their mind.

00:25:24.710 --> 00:25:27.460 align:middle line:10%
They would actually
probably lose their mind.

00:25:27.460 --> 00:25:30.875 align:middle line:10%
But we've created a completely
artificial environment.

00:25:30.875 --> 00:25:32.000 align:middle line:10%
Again, we take for granted.

00:25:32.000 --> 00:25:32.570 align:middle line:10%
We're used to it.

00:25:32.570 --> 00:25:33.410 align:middle line:10%
We're adaptable.

00:25:33.410 --> 00:25:35.680 align:middle line:10%
It's good for us.

00:25:35.680 --> 00:25:38.030 align:middle line:10%
But we must serve the
needs of this system.

00:25:38.030 --> 00:25:39.140 align:middle line:10%
What is this system?

00:25:39.140 --> 00:25:41.860 align:middle line:10%
It's an artificial
system that relies now

00:25:41.860 --> 00:25:44.230 align:middle line:10%
on a digital infrastructure.

00:25:44.230 --> 00:25:47.500 align:middle line:10%
International shipping has got
to be exactly a certain way.

00:25:47.500 --> 00:25:50.950 align:middle line:10%
Or those goods won't go from
China to here or wherever.

00:25:50.950 --> 00:25:54.140 align:middle line:10%
There's rules and bureaucracy
that must be in place.

00:25:54.140 --> 00:25:55.190 align:middle line:10%
That's the system.

00:25:55.190 --> 00:25:56.660 align:middle line:10%
You've got to serve that system.

00:25:56.660 --> 00:25:58.300 align:middle line:10%
We created it for our needs.

00:25:58.300 --> 00:25:59.720 align:middle line:10%
But now we must serve it.

00:25:59.720 --> 00:26:01.550 align:middle line:10%
And here's the real irony.

00:26:01.550 --> 00:26:06.970 align:middle line:10%
We have now created a system
with AI in which we are not

00:26:06.970 --> 00:26:09.450 align:middle line:10%
going to be necessary.

00:26:09.450 --> 00:26:11.840 align:middle line:10%
This is important to understand.

00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:14.580 align:middle line:10%
We like to think,
oh, well, we create

00:26:14.580 --> 00:26:16.270 align:middle line:10%
these systems for our benefit.

00:26:16.270 --> 00:26:18.400 align:middle line:10%
But that's not really true.

00:26:18.400 --> 00:26:20.220 align:middle line:10%
We think they're
for our benefit.

00:26:20.220 --> 00:26:21.760 align:middle line:10%
But we must serve their needs.

00:26:21.760 --> 00:26:25.140 align:middle line:10%
There is a logic to
the infrastructure

00:26:25.140 --> 00:26:27.840 align:middle line:10%
and the technology
that we have created.

00:26:27.840 --> 00:26:29.880 align:middle line:10%
And that logic is inexorable.

00:26:29.880 --> 00:26:32.610 align:middle line:10%
And it will be obeyed.

00:26:32.610 --> 00:26:34.110 align:middle line:10%
It will be obeyed.

00:26:34.110 --> 00:26:38.870 align:middle line:10%
The logic is for maximum
efficiency of itself.

00:26:38.870 --> 00:26:39.920 align:middle line:90%
And if--

00:26:39.920 --> 00:26:42.260 align:middle line:90%
So you have corporations.

00:26:42.260 --> 00:26:46.160 align:middle line:10%
It's like if you reincarnated
Buddha or Jesus Christ

00:26:46.160 --> 00:26:48.920 align:middle line:10%
and made them the
head of ExxonMobil.

00:26:48.920 --> 00:26:52.790 align:middle line:10%
Do you think they'd be able
to change a thing about how

00:26:52.790 --> 00:26:54.440 align:middle line:10%
that corporation is run?

00:26:54.440 --> 00:26:56.020 align:middle line:10%
No.

00:26:56.020 --> 00:26:57.250 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:26:57.250 --> 00:27:01.270 align:middle line:84%
The corporation has its
own inexorable logic

00:27:01.270 --> 00:27:03.650 align:middle line:90%
that must be followed.

00:27:03.650 --> 00:27:07.670 align:middle line:10%
And if the profits aren't there,
well, they get booted out.

00:27:07.670 --> 00:27:08.810 align:middle line:10%
They're no longer CEO.

00:27:08.810 --> 00:27:10.540 align:middle line:10%
And that's the reality.

00:27:10.540 --> 00:27:12.650 align:middle line:10%
So we must serve the system.

00:27:12.650 --> 00:27:14.090 align:middle line:10%
It has its own logic.

00:27:14.090 --> 00:27:17.590 align:middle line:10%
30 plus years ago, Bill
Joy, one of the co-founders

00:27:17.590 --> 00:27:21.163 align:middle line:10%
of Sun Microsystems, famously
said, hey, this AI, we

00:27:21.163 --> 00:27:23.080 align:middle line:10%
got to stop this right
now because this is not

00:27:23.080 --> 00:27:24.200 align:middle line:10%
going to go well for us.

00:27:24.200 --> 00:27:26.350 align:middle line:10%
It's going to-- and
everyone was looking at him

00:27:26.350 --> 00:27:29.270 align:middle line:10%
like, What drugs are you taking?

00:27:29.270 --> 00:27:33.850 align:middle line:10%
Like, how do you see this
as even remotely possible?

00:27:33.850 --> 00:27:36.100 align:middle line:10%
And indeed, there wasn't.

00:27:36.100 --> 00:27:38.200 align:middle line:10%
There wasn't any way
that anyone could see

00:27:38.200 --> 00:27:40.270 align:middle line:10%
because corporations compete.

00:27:40.270 --> 00:27:41.230 align:middle line:10%
Nations compete.

00:27:41.230 --> 00:27:42.440 align:middle line:10%
Militaries compete.

00:27:42.440 --> 00:27:44.420 align:middle line:10%
That has to be developed.

00:27:44.420 --> 00:27:47.390 align:middle line:10%
AI, from their point
of view, has to happen.

00:27:47.390 --> 00:27:50.130 align:middle line:10%
There is no way around it.

00:27:50.130 --> 00:27:53.620 align:middle line:84%
There are too many forces in
the world that were pushing it.

00:27:53.620 --> 00:27:58.050 align:middle line:84%
And so we as a
species are forced

00:27:58.050 --> 00:28:02.960 align:middle line:84%
to conform to the
needs of the system.

00:28:02.960 --> 00:28:04.300 align:middle line:90%
We serve the system.

00:28:04.300 --> 00:28:07.900 align:middle line:84%
That's, in a nutshell,
my thought on that.

00:28:07.900 --> 00:28:12.750 align:middle line:84%
So transhumanism, post-humanism,
it is becoming a fact.

00:28:12.750 --> 00:28:17.060 align:middle line:10%
When will it become a
reality, a true reality?

00:28:17.060 --> 00:28:17.860 align:middle line:10%
I don't know.

00:28:17.860 --> 00:28:20.620 align:middle line:10%
I don't know if it's 20
years, maybe less, maybe more.

00:28:20.620 --> 00:28:22.060 align:middle line:10%
I don't know.

00:28:22.060 --> 00:28:28.300 align:middle line:10%
But for the same reasons that
AI is a fact, which will be--

00:28:28.300 --> 00:28:31.150 align:middle line:10%
you can imagine parents
wanting their kids

00:28:31.150 --> 00:28:33.267 align:middle line:10%
to get maybe a little
bit of extra advantage.

00:28:33.267 --> 00:28:35.350 align:middle line:10%
We'll do a little genetic
tweaking here, make them

00:28:35.350 --> 00:28:40.620 align:middle line:10%
a little bit better immune
system or a little smarter

00:28:40.620 --> 00:28:41.910 align:middle line:10%
or whatever.

00:28:41.910 --> 00:28:44.790 align:middle line:10%
I guarantee you there's going
to be negative repercussions

00:28:44.790 --> 00:28:46.373 align:middle line:10%
that no one is predicting.

00:28:46.373 --> 00:28:47.790 align:middle line:10%
We're going to see
"Jurassic Park"

00:28:47.790 --> 00:28:51.060 align:middle line:10%
on a wide scale in the sense
of unintended consequences.

00:28:51.060 --> 00:28:51.990 align:middle line:10%
That will happen.

00:28:51.990 --> 00:28:55.670 align:middle line:10%
But it will not stop
this from happening.

00:28:55.670 --> 00:28:58.260 align:middle line:10%
Transhumanism,
you mark my words,

00:28:58.260 --> 00:29:00.900 align:middle line:10%
that's going to happen in
the next generation and two

00:29:00.900 --> 00:29:02.680 align:middle line:10%
generations and then beyond.

00:29:02.680 --> 00:29:04.030 align:middle line:10%
It's off to the races.

00:29:04.030 --> 00:29:07.480 align:middle line:10%
So what is changing
in our world?

00:29:07.480 --> 00:29:10.020 align:middle line:10%
Well, pretty much everything
is changing, right down

00:29:10.020 --> 00:29:14.170 align:middle line:10%
to the fundamentals of what
it means to be a human being,

00:29:14.170 --> 00:29:16.560 align:middle line:10%
that is, your family relations.

00:29:16.560 --> 00:29:19.380 align:middle line:84%
You think about
how families were.

00:29:19.380 --> 00:29:21.450 align:middle line:84%
Back in the old
country, my mom, they're

00:29:21.450 --> 00:29:24.780 align:middle line:84%
all Italian Americans-- cheek
pinching, back slapping,

00:29:24.780 --> 00:29:25.660 align:middle line:90%
in your face.

00:29:25.660 --> 00:29:27.930 align:middle line:90%
Hey, Richie, get over here.

00:29:27.930 --> 00:29:28.860 align:middle line:10%
I grew up with that.

00:29:28.860 --> 00:29:30.700 align:middle line:10%
And I love and
miss those people.

00:29:30.700 --> 00:29:31.550 align:middle line:10%
They were the best.

00:29:31.550 --> 00:29:32.350 align:middle line:10%
They were the best.

00:29:32.350 --> 00:29:34.950 align:middle line:10%
And I'm sure all of you
have your own version

00:29:34.950 --> 00:29:37.000 align:middle line:10%
of that kind of family memory.

00:29:37.000 --> 00:29:41.870 align:middle line:10%
And I would like to think
that that will continue.

00:29:41.870 --> 00:29:45.430 align:middle line:10%
But there's a little nagging
concern that it won't.

00:29:45.430 --> 00:29:46.790 align:middle line:10%
Something's changing.

00:29:46.790 --> 00:29:51.070 align:middle line:10%
Family relationships
are changing.

00:29:51.070 --> 00:29:55.910 align:middle line:10%
How we form our communities
is fundamentally changing.

00:29:55.910 --> 00:29:59.170 align:middle line:84%
These are basic facts of what
it means to be a human being--

00:29:59.170 --> 00:30:04.690 align:middle line:84%
how we find our husband or wife
or boyfriend or girlfriend,

00:30:04.690 --> 00:30:06.870 align:middle line:90%
how we court and mate.

00:30:06.870 --> 00:30:09.950 align:middle line:10%
But actually-- I said
husband and wife at first.

00:30:09.950 --> 00:30:12.950 align:middle line:10%
But that's going away.

00:30:12.950 --> 00:30:16.040 align:middle line:10%
You see, the world that we've
created destroys marriages.

00:30:16.040 --> 00:30:18.060 align:middle line:10%
I mean, it just destroys them.

00:30:18.060 --> 00:30:19.060 align:middle line:10%
We see it.

00:30:19.060 --> 00:30:22.230 align:middle line:10%
So that's changing.

00:30:22.230 --> 00:30:24.660 align:middle line:10%
Food, how you do your food--

00:30:24.660 --> 00:30:26.080 align:middle line:10%
I'm sure some of you are great.

00:30:26.080 --> 00:30:29.010 align:middle line:10%
I know some of you
are amazing cooks.

00:30:29.010 --> 00:30:32.140 align:middle line:10%
But a lot of people
don't cook anymore.

00:30:32.140 --> 00:30:36.360 align:middle line:10%
We've become sort of
divorced from our food--

00:30:36.360 --> 00:30:38.320 align:middle line:10%
how we eat it,
how we prepare it.

00:30:38.320 --> 00:30:39.780 align:middle line:10%
All of that's different.

00:30:39.780 --> 00:30:43.200 align:middle line:10%
We have a different
relationship to something

00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:46.590 align:middle line:10%
as basic and fundamental
as the food that we eat.

00:30:46.590 --> 00:30:51.350 align:middle line:10%
How kids grow up, how
we look at each other--

00:30:51.350 --> 00:30:53.530 align:middle line:10%
that's changing.

00:30:53.530 --> 00:30:56.300 align:middle line:84%
That's why I picked this
photograph, this picture here,

00:30:56.300 --> 00:30:57.100 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:30:57.100 --> 00:30:59.110 align:middle line:84%
How many times
have you seen that?

00:30:59.110 --> 00:31:03.830 align:middle line:10%
And our level of privacy
is dramatically changing.

00:31:03.830 --> 00:31:05.990 align:middle line:10%
You may not feel it in
your day to day life.

00:31:05.990 --> 00:31:06.820 align:middle line:10%
I understand that.

00:31:06.820 --> 00:31:09.260 align:middle line:10%
If you're a public person,
you probably do feel it.

00:31:09.260 --> 00:31:12.580 align:middle line:10%
But even if you're someone
who's got a Facebook page

00:31:12.580 --> 00:31:15.760 align:middle line:10%
and your family and friends
are on it, you feel it anyway.

00:31:15.760 --> 00:31:17.410 align:middle line:10%
You feel it anyway.

00:31:17.410 --> 00:31:18.430 align:middle line:10%
You know.

00:31:18.430 --> 00:31:20.630 align:middle line:10%
OK, there's all these eyes here.

00:31:20.630 --> 00:31:24.110 align:middle line:10%
And that just gets
bigger and bigger.

00:31:24.110 --> 00:31:26.480 align:middle line:10%
So these aren't trivial things.

00:31:26.480 --> 00:31:29.112 align:middle line:10%
These are fundamental
things about what

00:31:29.112 --> 00:31:30.320 align:middle line:10%
it means to be a human being.

00:31:30.320 --> 00:31:32.680 align:middle line:10%
And all of it's
changing, basically

00:31:32.680 --> 00:31:34.480 align:middle line:10%
in the snap of a finger.

00:31:34.480 --> 00:31:37.520 align:middle line:10%
And you could say
these are good changes.

00:31:37.520 --> 00:31:42.410 align:middle line:10%
Yeah, some of them are-- we love
them all when they seem new.

00:31:42.410 --> 00:31:45.015 align:middle line:10%
But then we see a
lot of the effects.

00:31:45.015 --> 00:31:49.260 align:middle line:90%


00:31:49.260 --> 00:31:53.190 align:middle line:10%
On a more basic political,
social level, other things

00:31:53.190 --> 00:31:55.740 align:middle line:10%
are also changing--
the internet.

00:31:55.740 --> 00:31:59.310 align:middle line:10%
Maybe what I'm saying on the top
here is a little extreme but not

00:31:59.310 --> 00:32:00.170 align:middle line:10%
too much.

00:32:00.170 --> 00:32:02.310 align:middle line:10%
I say it's turning back into TV.

00:32:02.310 --> 00:32:03.670 align:middle line:90%
OK, not totally.

00:32:03.670 --> 00:32:05.860 align:middle line:90%
It's not quite like 1980s.

00:32:05.860 --> 00:32:07.680 align:middle line:90%
Ugh, remember that.

00:32:07.680 --> 00:32:11.470 align:middle line:84%
There's a little bit more on
the web than 1980s television.

00:32:11.470 --> 00:32:14.220 align:middle line:10%
But you can see
the guard rails--

00:32:14.220 --> 00:32:18.150 align:middle line:10%
and that's the word we hear
all the time-- are there.

00:32:18.150 --> 00:32:22.980 align:middle line:10%
You know, the monitoring
against harm to you.

00:32:22.980 --> 00:32:25.360 align:middle line:10%
If you read the wrong
thing, that could harm you.

00:32:25.360 --> 00:32:28.450 align:middle line:10%
So we need to curate your news.

00:32:28.450 --> 00:32:30.920 align:middle line:10%
You hear that word
a lot-- curating.

00:32:30.920 --> 00:32:33.780 align:middle line:10%
That's just a nice word
for censoring, of course.

00:32:33.780 --> 00:32:35.643 align:middle line:10%
It's turning back
into TV, only worse.

00:32:35.643 --> 00:32:37.810 align:middle line:10%
And the worst part is that
it's looking back at you.

00:32:37.810 --> 00:32:40.140 align:middle line:10%
That's like the Big
Brother out of Orwell.

00:32:40.140 --> 00:32:44.500 align:middle line:10%
Your internet's looking at you
every time you're on there.

00:32:44.500 --> 00:32:46.550 align:middle line:10%
So that's not too cool.

00:32:46.550 --> 00:32:47.550 align:middle line:10%
But that's happening.

00:32:47.550 --> 00:32:49.760 align:middle line:10%
The surveillance
state is all around.

00:32:49.760 --> 00:32:51.950 align:middle line:10%
Again, it tries to
make itself invisible.

00:32:51.950 --> 00:32:53.560 align:middle line:10%
It does a good job
a lot of the time.

00:32:53.560 --> 00:32:55.120 align:middle line:10%
But it's all there.

00:32:55.120 --> 00:32:56.210 align:middle line:10%
It's always there.

00:32:56.210 --> 00:32:58.800 align:middle line:10%
And you know it's there.

00:32:58.800 --> 00:33:00.550 align:middle line:84%
And along with that,
of course, everything

00:33:00.550 --> 00:33:04.690 align:middle line:84%
else that follows-- a radical
reduction in permissible speech.

00:33:04.690 --> 00:33:06.830 align:middle line:84%
I just read an
article a week ago.

00:33:06.830 --> 00:33:09.250 align:middle line:84%
A couple of women in the UK
got arrested because they put

00:33:09.250 --> 00:33:10.510 align:middle line:90%
the wrong thing on Facebook.

00:33:10.510 --> 00:33:12.070 align:middle line:90%
And they're in jail.

00:33:12.070 --> 00:33:14.170 align:middle line:10%
They expressed the
wrong opinion, whatever.

00:33:14.170 --> 00:33:16.128 align:middle line:10%
And I'm not going to get
into that whole thing.

00:33:16.128 --> 00:33:23.450 align:middle line:10%
But UK arresting and imprisoning
two women for a Facebook post--

00:33:23.450 --> 00:33:26.050 align:middle line:10%
I mean, this is insane.

00:33:26.050 --> 00:33:28.000 align:middle line:10%
By the way, the English
Commonwealth nations

00:33:28.000 --> 00:33:31.270 align:middle line:10%
are some of the
worst now by far in--

00:33:31.270 --> 00:33:33.280 align:middle line:10%
I mean, I feel like,
how different are you

00:33:33.280 --> 00:33:34.670 align:middle line:10%
from China at this point?

00:33:34.670 --> 00:33:35.810 align:middle line:10%
Not very.

00:33:35.810 --> 00:33:37.450 align:middle line:10%
Not very.

00:33:37.450 --> 00:33:38.803 align:middle line:10%
The US is still better off.

00:33:38.803 --> 00:33:40.220 align:middle line:10%
We still have the
First Amendment.

00:33:40.220 --> 00:33:41.650 align:middle line:10%
I mean, thank God.

00:33:41.650 --> 00:33:43.870 align:middle line:10%
That's our saving grace.

00:33:43.870 --> 00:33:49.390 align:middle line:10%
But the UK, Canada,
Australia, and New Zealand--

00:33:49.390 --> 00:33:51.130 align:middle line:10%
not so great.

00:33:51.130 --> 00:33:52.570 align:middle line:10%
Not so great.

00:33:52.570 --> 00:33:54.790 align:middle line:10%
Digital control over
your money will increase.

00:33:54.790 --> 00:33:57.560 align:middle line:84%
And that can happen
at any time now.

00:33:57.560 --> 00:34:00.490 align:middle line:84%
And it will be more likely
once you start seeing

00:34:00.490 --> 00:34:01.793 align:middle line:90%
digital currencies rolled out.

00:34:01.793 --> 00:34:02.710 align:middle line:90%
They're not there yet.

00:34:02.710 --> 00:34:04.120 align:middle line:90%
But that will happen.

00:34:04.120 --> 00:34:06.010 align:middle line:10%
The whole issue of
AI and employment--

00:34:06.010 --> 00:34:08.110 align:middle line:10%
I mentioned before
the fear of job loss.

00:34:08.110 --> 00:34:10.070 align:middle line:10%
And obviously, that will happen.

00:34:10.070 --> 00:34:11.980 align:middle line:10%
Yeah, jobs will be created.

00:34:11.980 --> 00:34:16.449 align:middle line:10%
But it will really be the
same amount that are lost,

00:34:16.449 --> 00:34:20.199 align:middle line:10%
maybe in the long term with a
radical reduction in population

00:34:20.199 --> 00:34:21.500 align:middle line:10%
and a reorganization.

00:34:21.500 --> 00:34:24.100 align:middle line:10%
But for right now,
for our lifetimes,

00:34:24.100 --> 00:34:27.610 align:middle line:10%
I think it's going to be very,
very difficult, very tough.

00:34:27.610 --> 00:34:30.969 align:middle line:10%
And that's a whole other
problem that we are not

00:34:30.969 --> 00:34:34.909 align:middle line:10%
dealing with very well
as a society at all.

00:34:34.909 --> 00:34:39.760 align:middle line:10%
And then the BCI,
Brain-Computer Interface--

00:34:39.760 --> 00:34:40.758 align:middle line:10%
can you imagine?

00:34:40.758 --> 00:34:42.800 align:middle line:10%
I mean, let's just put
some things together here.

00:34:42.800 --> 00:34:46.295 align:middle line:10%
So I'm having a conversation
with my BCI with some friend.

00:34:46.295 --> 00:34:49.010 align:middle line:10%


00:34:49.010 --> 00:34:51.409 align:middle line:10%
And then you've got
AI algorithms probably

00:34:51.409 --> 00:34:53.929 align:middle line:10%
monitoring every conversation.

00:34:53.929 --> 00:34:56.840 align:middle line:10%
I mean, how far away
are we from a situation

00:34:56.840 --> 00:35:00.230 align:middle line:10%
where an algorithm is going
to monitor what you say

00:35:00.230 --> 00:35:04.280 align:middle line:10%
and give a safer output
because what you're saying

00:35:04.280 --> 00:35:06.270 align:middle line:10%
is deemed harmful?

00:35:06.270 --> 00:35:09.060 align:middle line:10%
I'm starting to use
the DALL-E art program.

00:35:09.060 --> 00:35:10.890 align:middle line:10%
Canva has got a really
nice feature on it.

00:35:10.890 --> 00:35:12.510 align:middle line:10%
And I can create
some really cool art.

00:35:12.510 --> 00:35:16.200 align:middle line:10%
And I'm putting in totally
like tame subjects.

00:35:16.200 --> 00:35:18.560 align:middle line:10%
And it's telling me,
you can't do this.

00:35:18.560 --> 00:35:19.360 align:middle line:10%
You can't do that.

00:35:19.360 --> 00:35:21.360 align:middle line:10%
This violates art.

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:24.210 align:middle line:10%
I'm just trying to create
a guy with a cowboy hat.

00:35:24.210 --> 00:35:25.210 align:middle line:10%
What's the problem here?

00:35:25.210 --> 00:35:28.000 align:middle line:10%
But it won't do it frequently.

00:35:28.000 --> 00:35:30.550 align:middle line:10%
So you already see
this happening.

00:35:30.550 --> 00:35:35.010 align:middle line:84%
And I can at least envision
this going really, really south

00:35:35.010 --> 00:35:36.437 align:middle line:90%
for us.

00:35:36.437 --> 00:35:37.770 align:middle line:90%
We're here in the United States.

00:35:37.770 --> 00:35:41.077 align:middle line:84%
And we're used to a certain
amount of freedom and privacy.

00:35:41.077 --> 00:35:42.660 align:middle line:10%
But first of all,
there's a whole rest

00:35:42.660 --> 00:35:43.618 align:middle line:10%
of the world out there.

00:35:43.618 --> 00:35:45.330 align:middle line:10%
And they're not going to get it.

00:35:45.330 --> 00:35:47.440 align:middle line:10%
They will not get the
protections that we have.

00:35:47.440 --> 00:35:49.340 align:middle line:10%
They will not get
those protections.

00:35:49.340 --> 00:35:50.910 align:middle line:10%
Not gonna happen for them.

00:35:50.910 --> 00:35:54.990 align:middle line:10%
But secondly, how long do you
think we're going to keep ours?

00:35:54.990 --> 00:35:57.480 align:middle line:84%
I hear people saying all the
time, well, we need Elon Musk.

00:35:57.480 --> 00:35:59.100 align:middle line:90%
We need to put in safeguards.

00:35:59.100 --> 00:36:00.810 align:middle line:84%
And yeah, all
right, yeah, we all

00:36:00.810 --> 00:36:03.115 align:middle line:84%
heard you got to
put in safeguards.

00:36:03.115 --> 00:36:05.490 align:middle line:84%
How long do you think those
safeguards are going to last?

00:36:05.490 --> 00:36:08.220 align:middle line:10%
One generation,
maybe two generations

00:36:08.220 --> 00:36:10.890 align:middle line:10%
if we're really lucky, 40 years?

00:36:10.890 --> 00:36:12.738 align:middle line:10%
Well, eventually,
they're going to go away

00:36:12.738 --> 00:36:14.280 align:middle line:10%
because, you know
why, there's always

00:36:14.280 --> 00:36:16.790 align:middle line:10%
going to be a new crisis
that takes them away.

00:36:16.790 --> 00:36:19.290 align:middle line:10%
It's always going to be another
one right around the corner.

00:36:19.290 --> 00:36:23.060 align:middle line:84%
Political crisis-- well, we
got an election coming up.

00:36:23.060 --> 00:36:25.087 align:middle line:90%
Oh, my dear God.

00:36:25.087 --> 00:36:26.420 align:middle line:90%
Don't even get me started there.

00:36:26.420 --> 00:36:30.490 align:middle line:84%
But I'm bringing it up
here because we've all

00:36:30.490 --> 00:36:33.830 align:middle line:84%
gone into crazy mode in
the last decade or so.

00:36:33.830 --> 00:36:38.050 align:middle line:10%
And you can see, can't you?

00:36:38.050 --> 00:36:41.940 align:middle line:10%
The justification
that a government

00:36:41.940 --> 00:36:47.700 align:middle line:10%
could have to regulate your
speech and your person even more

00:36:47.700 --> 00:36:54.050 align:middle line:10%
to prevent harm from coming
to the rest of society.

00:36:54.050 --> 00:36:57.170 align:middle line:10%
They're using that word harm
all the time for all sorts

00:36:57.170 --> 00:36:59.480 align:middle line:10%
of inappropriate ways.

00:36:59.480 --> 00:37:00.510 align:middle line:10%
But they'll do it.

00:37:00.510 --> 00:37:03.620 align:middle line:10%
So there's, in other
words, many crises

00:37:03.620 --> 00:37:09.650 align:middle line:10%
that can happen that will prompt
central powers to exacerbate

00:37:09.650 --> 00:37:13.010 align:middle line:10%
the draconian controls
that they're already

00:37:13.010 --> 00:37:18.260 align:middle line:10%
exerting over the population,
I guess, or biological.

00:37:18.260 --> 00:37:21.710 align:middle line:10%
We had COVID just a
couple of years ago.

00:37:21.710 --> 00:37:24.740 align:middle line:84%
Do we think that's never
going to happen again?

00:37:24.740 --> 00:37:27.410 align:middle line:90%
You can see.

00:37:27.410 --> 00:37:29.390 align:middle line:84%
In some labs, someone's
cooking up something.

00:37:29.390 --> 00:37:31.730 align:middle line:84%
And who knows where
that will end?

00:37:31.730 --> 00:37:33.300 align:middle line:90%
So we're just primed.

00:37:33.300 --> 00:37:35.040 align:middle line:84%
We're primed for
another great crisis.

00:37:35.040 --> 00:37:37.665 align:middle line:84%
It could be a combination of any
of the above or something else

00:37:37.665 --> 00:37:39.380 align:middle line:90%
I'm not even thinking about.

00:37:39.380 --> 00:37:44.630 align:middle line:10%
One more great crisis, maybe
two or three more great crises--

00:37:44.630 --> 00:37:47.810 align:middle line:10%
maybe that's happening
because we're

00:37:47.810 --> 00:37:51.920 align:middle line:10%
seeing this transformation
of the human species.

00:37:51.920 --> 00:37:58.500 align:middle line:10%
And to create this end result,
that's what's happening.

00:37:58.500 --> 00:38:02.150 align:middle line:90%
